page.title: 04Buildings in Marsworth
page.content: {Lower Ickenield Way}_Bungalows, Semidetached private and council houses,Rothschilds Village Hall ,extended in1977. {The Crescent}_(1950)Semidetached Council houses and Old peoples Bungalows. {Vicarage Road}_Main road through Village(Rothschilds).Old 17th century houses,Orchard development of Individual Houses(1940),Old peoples bungalows,Church,School,White House(1940),Rothschild Houses,New detached Houses(1970),Semidetached (1930),Shop {Vicarage Gardens}_Sold as 9 Executive detached Houses,some now extended. Built on site of old Vicarage. {Stepnells}_4 bed detached(1970),new development off it.{Norvic Road}_3 bed semis(1940) most now extended.{Lukes {Lea}2 bed semis ,4 bed detached(1970)
